+------------------+--------------------------+
                   |
                   v
+------------------+--------------------------+
| Open Video Capture                          |
+------------------+--------------------------+
                   |
                   v
+------------------+--------------------------+
| Loop over Frames from Video                 |
+------------------+--------------------------+
                   |
                   v
+------------------+--------------------------+
| Detect and Recognize Faces in the Frame     |
+------------------+--------------------------+
                   |
                   v
+------------------+--------------------------+
| If Face Recognized                          |
|   - Mark Attendance                         |
|   - Send Authorization Message              |
+------------------+--------------------------+
                   |
                   v
+------------------+--------------------------+
| If Face Not Recognized                      |
|   - Send Unauthorization Message            |
+------------------+--------------------------+
                   |
                   v
+------------------+--------------------------+
| Display Frame with Recognition Results      |
+------------------+--------------------------+
                   |
                   v
+------------------+--------------------------+
| Quit Program                                |
